gn, vibrant display, and killer battery life, it’s a steal at its current $237 price on Amazon. While some people think Motorola could’ve added fancier stylus features like the Samsung S Pen’s Bluetooth tricks and pressure sensitivity, getting a stylus included for free is already a solid win, especially when you'd usually only see that on premium phones like the Samsung S24 Ultra.",
